{"tid":2498511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"活29年沒月經！女求診發現嘸子宮　醫一看驚：下面有睪丸","createTime":"2021-04-21T08:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T08:25:27.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c1efbfd01fb9e0ec57b4dcd7235c619d3273f7c","tid":2498511,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"國際中心／魏聖凌報導<br />\n<br />\n活了29年，女子竟發現自己根本不是女的！越南近日出現一起離奇病例，一名女子因成年後驚覺月經遲遲未來，擔心地前往醫院求診，沒想到卻發現自己根本沒有子宮，甚至還擁有男性的生殖器官，才發現自己原來是男兒身。<br />\n<br />\n根據越南媒體《Tiin》報導，河南一名29歲女子，小時候出生時是一名健康的寶寶，院方在性別欄位中登記為「女」，家人也相當開心迎來這名女娃。不過女子長大進入青春期後，儘管外貌及乳房發育和一般女性沒有差別，但初經卻遲遲未來，甚至到了18歲仍毫無動靜，讓他感到相當困惑，原以為是原發性閉經，沒想到經醫師診斷後，才知道自己沒有子宮且陰道畸形，讓他深受打擊。<br />\n<br />\n該名女子因自己的身體缺陷而陷入低潮，加上29年來無法和男友發生性關係，因此對自己的身體越來越困惑，近日受不了到醫院接受檢查，沒想到竟發現了天大的秘密。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/13/2553103-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F13%2F2553103-PH.jpg&h=0975806d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，該名女子經醫院精密檢查後，竟發現自己有XY染色體，代表他其實是男性，讓活了29年的他瞬間變為男兒身。女子事後求助整形外科醫院，想做陰道手術，才發現自己不但沒有子宮，尿道兩側還有令醫師難以分辨的結構，透過切片檢查後才發現原來是睪丸，應為假性雌雄同體（假陰陽症）。<br />\n<br />\n面對這場大挑戰，醫療團隊也邀請性別與基因專家加入。由於他對女性身分較為自在，因此醫師決定以腹腔鏡手術為他切除睪丸，並為他做陰道整形手術，讓活了29年的他能真正成為一名女人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=928148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D928148&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dKooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=2165a4ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D928148&h=8d8c8223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=928148</a>"},{"pid":"bf162ebddd5b01ad0d1edc2acc5e63220dcfd41a","tid":2498511,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"事主:me竟然是個boy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e4fe88cf2e3afddf7972929135184477f0bf14","tid":2498511,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"唔知點解東南亞係特別多呢d性別基因/表觀有問題嘅人"},{"pid":"317df1be4822a5c26c0e56502c52edf37353d5b9","tid":2498511,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:22:46.000Z","msg":"阿安應該幫到佢<br />\n因為.....<br />\n安能辨佢是雄雌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dc9485c22725868fb10ac750763906cf30023b","tid":2498511,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317df1be4822a5c26c0e56502c52edf37353d5b9","tid":2498511,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:22:46.000Z","msg":"阿安應該幫到佢<br />\n因為.....<br />\n安能辨佢是雄雌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"哈哈"},{"pid":"d3f1252839c51763ded13027d7baef3c3c122c1a","tid":2498511,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:25:10.000Z","msg":"儘管外貌及乳房發育和一般女性沒有差別<br />\n大奶奶呢?大奶奶係邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920529840c8221e17f1088932f46eb471c2fc39c","tid":2498511,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">河南一名29歲女子....加上29年來無法和男友發生性關係</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}